{
  "stem": "24195.4",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it was pretty heavy wire from one of the hangars to another one.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And suddenly, they ordered us to take it off, and they commanded about-- take 20, 30, 40 guys.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know how heavy it was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The guards said take it off.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It became a tug of war.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It took-- 25 guys pulled on that side, and 25 or 30 guys on the other side.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Before you know, the dumb thing split.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "I can't believe how it happened, but it split.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Well, they couldn't replace things like that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This was another you know-- another-- another incident where it was impossible that would-- hurting the war effort.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Exactly.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was done purposely.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But nobody talked about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was just quietly- that was passive-- what you call passive resistance.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Active resistance we couldn't do.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They would shoot.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They would-- they would take, certainly, stern measures, I mean, if we openly showed our defiance.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But this-- they thought we were stupid.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know-- honestly, I cannot believe.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "One day I was ordered to take cement sacks, because for the concrete mixer off of the truck.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "When the guard goes up-- one of these Organization Todt people goes up-- and he says-- he has a line of us standing up.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Everybody is supposed to throw down a sack.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't how heavy it was, maybe 100 pounds, maybe heavier.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Now do I look like the guy that you can throw from a truck?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Throw and expect me to catch it?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I dropped the darn thing.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Purposely?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And you know what-- purposely.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And you know what happens when you drop a-- a-- a bag of cement?",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It just splits open, wide open and into dust.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So then another one, another one of those was ruined.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They didn't say anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
